txt.en: Gaerdring and Gaerthel have been defeated and half of the Great Barrows key has been claimed.
Great Barrow -- The Gate to Sambrog
Access to the depths of the Great Barrow and the gaunt-man Sambrog is gated by a key. One half lies within the maze, the other with Thadúr.
Defeat Thadúr the Ravager and claim half of the key
Defeat Gaerdring and Gaerthel and claim half of the key.
Thadúr the Ravager has fallen and you have claimed his half of the Great Barrows key.
